        "acceptedAnswer": {
          "@type": "Answer",
          "text": "It depends on your stage. Brands establishing a baseline benefit most from broad platform coverage — knowing which AI engines cite them across the full landscape. Brands with an existing programme and a clear content strategy benefit more from deep citation tracking: URL-level attribution, response-position data, and sentiment accuracy. In practice, the two dimensions are not mutually exclusive, but when budget forces a trade-off, match the priority to your programme's immediate measurement objective."
        }
      },
      {
        "@type": "Question",
        "name": "Why does the pricing model matter when comparing GEO tools?",
        "acceptedAnswer": {
          "@type": "Answer",
