        "acceptedAnswer": {
          "@type": "Answer",
          "text": "Assess integrations in terms of the workflows they unlock rather than the raw count of connectors. The most practically useful integrations connect the GEO tool to your existing analytics infrastructure (GA4, Looker Studio, or your data warehouse), to your content publishing workflow (so citation insights flow to writers and editors), and to your SEO platform (so traditional authority metrics can be correlated with AI citation rates). A tool with ten integrations you will never use is less valuable than one with two integrations that directly improve your reporting and content decision-making."
